What?!

87
00:06:50.747 --> 00:06:53.177
Thank you for getting it back from him.

88
00:06:53.387 --> 00:06:54.437
No problem.

89
00:06:54.437 --> 00:06:57.687
By the way, why are you
carrying so much cash?

90
00:06:58.607 --> 00:06:59.647
I...

91
