100
00:07:33.287 --> 00:07:35.687
Huh? She doesn't have her bag with her.

101
00:07:36.097 --> 00:07:37.437
You're right.

102
00:07:37.977 --> 00:07:40.437
Hey, what happened to your bag?

103
00:07:40.907 --> 00:07:42.287
I left it.

104
00:07:42.287 --> 00:07:44.717
What? But why?

105
00:07:45.947 --> 00:07:47.947
Why did you leave it?

106
00:07:51.407 --> 00:07:54.197
The truth is, that was ransom money.

107
00:07:56.997 --> 00:07:58.077
Where did you leave it?

108
00:07:58.387 --> 00:07:59.707
In the parking lot.

109
00:08:01.137 --> 00:08:02.367
Where?

110
00:08:04.097 --> 00:08:05.047
Over there.

111
00:08:08.527 --> 00:08:10.507
We're too late.

112
00:08:12.417 --> 00:08:16.747
Good. Now Manabu-san
will be returned safely.

113
00:08:18.857 --> 00:08:20.557
I did the right thing, right?

114
00:08:20.927 --> 00:08:25.067
They'll release the hostage because
I gave them the money, right?

115
00:08:25.067 --> 00:08:27.067
No. It's possible that...

116
00:08:28.457 --> 00:08:29.697
What?

117
00:08:29.917 --> 00:08:33.277
It's possible the culprit has
no further use for the hostage,

118
00:08:33.277 --> 00:08:35.947
and no reason to leave them alive.

119
00:08:37.067 --> 00:08:38.517
But...

120
00:08:38.517 --> 00:08:41.127
Ran, call the police.

121
00:08:41.127 --> 00:08:41.967
Okay.

122
