Your clothes are dirty. Change into these.

195
00:12:52.324 --> 00:12:53.714
Thank you.

196
00:12:54.454 --> 00:12:58.264
Sir, I'm sorry for the
inconvenience I caused.

197
00:12:59.074 --> 00:13:02.724
How could you inconvenience us?
You're a plague on this company.

198
00:13:03.184 --> 00:13:07.894
Dad, Manabu-san didn't ask to be kidnapped.

199
00:13:08.114 --> 00:13:10.314
Yes, but...

200
00:13:10.734 --> 00:13:14.774
The president can't talk back to
Mari-chan because he adores her.

201
00:13:15.244 --> 00:13:18.154
Although it's a different story
when it comes to boyfriends.

202
00:13:18.704 --> 00:13:22.164
So she's your typical sheltered daughter.

203
00:13:23.234 --> 00:13:29.534
Excuse the interruption, but Manabu-san,
I'm glad you're all right.

204
00:13:29.534 --> 00:13:30.704
Who are you?

205
00:13:31.104 --> 00:13:34.324
I'm Mori Kogoro, a detective.

206
00:13:34.324 --> 00:13:35.654
A detective?

207
00:13:35.654 --> 00:13:38.964
I heard the kidnapper hasn't been caught yet.

208
00:13:39.314 --> 00:13:41.504
I'll help in any way I can.

209
00:13:41.954 --> 00:13:45.644
But I was blindfolded the whole time.

210
00:13:45.644 --> 00:13:47.704
I didn't see the culprit's face.

211
00:13:47.704 --> 00:13:50.044
Do you recall their voice?

212
00:13:50.044 --> 00:13:53.734
No. They used some kind
of device to modify it.

213
00:13:54.454 --> 00:13:56.734
So we have no clues to
the culprit's identity.

214
00:13:57.024 --> 00:13:59.254
You truly are useless.

215
00:13:59.974 --> 00:14:01.114
I'm sorry.

216
00:14:01.344 --> 00:14:04.864
Manabu-san, where and
when were you kidnapped?

217
00:14:05.584 --> 00:14:08.874
I believe it was around nine this morning.

218
00:14:08.874 --> 00:14:11.294
I think I was on my way to the office.

219
00:14:11.594 --> 00:14:17.504
Maybe that means the culprit was
familiar with your regular routine.

220
00:14:18.024 --> 00:14:22.324
If that's true, then it's possible
the kidnapper is an acquaintance.

221
00:14:22.324 --> 00:14:25.294
And it's possible they used a voice changer

222
00:14:25.294 --> 00:14:28.644
because Manabu-san would've been
very familiar with their voice.

223
00:14:32.754 --> 00:14:35.894
You think we did it?

224
00:14:36.244 --> 00:14:39.244
We're just discussing possibilities.

225
00:14:39.244 --> 00:14:42.904
By the way, where were you
around nine this morning?

226
00:14:43.194 --> 00:14:46.014
I was still in bed.

227
00:14:46.014 --> 00:14:48.344
Can anyone verify that?

228
00:14:50.724 --> 00:14:54.334
I saw Mari-chan sleeping.

229
00:14:54.334 --> 00:14:58.174
Her door was open while I was cleaning
this morning, and I caught a glimpse of her.

230
00:14:59.224 --> 00:15:02.044
I was preparing for work at the workshop.

231
00:15:02.044 --> 00:15:05.054
I met Yuko-san when she came to clean.

232
00:15:05.504 --> 00:15:06.984
That's right.

233
00:15:06.984 --> 00:15:11.294
Which means you're able to
verify each other's stories.

234
00:15:11.294 --> 00:15:13.174
You all have alibis.

235
00:15:13.694 --> 00:15:15.314
Sir, what about you?

236
00:15:15.754 --> 00:15:19.254
I was passed out drunk.

237
00:15:19.794 --> 00:15:22.574
Yuko-san, did you see the president?

238
00:15:22.894 --> 00:15:23.734
No.

239
00:15:24.354 --> 00:15:27.824
In other words, you have no
one to verify your alibi.

240
00:15:28.094 --> 00:15:29.624
W-Wait a minute.

241
00:15:29.624 --> 00:15:34.814
Maybe so, but we were right here when
the ransom money was handed off.

242
00:15:34.814 --> 00:15:36.374
We couldn't have done it.

243
00:15:37.164 --> 00:15:38.874
That's true.

244
00:15:38.874 --> 00:15:42.504
Which means the culprit is
someone not currently present.

245
00:15:43.634 --> 00:15:46.704
Mari, don't you think he's suspicious?

246
00:15:46.704 --> 00:15:48.114
He who?

247
00:15:48.114 --> 00:15:51.514
That nasty pest that keeps bugging Mari.

248
00:15:51.834 --> 00:15:53.784
Don't say that about him.

249
00:15:53.784 --> 00:15:56.204
Takumi-san is my boyfriend.

250
00:15:57.214 --> 00:15:59.024
I'll never accept it.

251
00:15:59.284 --> 00:16:01.524
In any case, tell him to
come here immediately!

252
00:16:12.954 --> 00:16:15.834
Mari, why did you want me to come to...

253
00:16:17.744 --> 00:16:20.424
Are you Kondo Takumi-san?

254
