00:16:34.564 --> 00:16:38.484
You're accusing me of
kidnapping? Give me a break.

262
00:16:38.484 --> 00:16:40.614
He's right. That's awful.

263
00:16:40.614 --> 00:16:45.274
You only approached Mari for my money,
and you're still playing dumb?

264
00:16:45.574 --> 00:16:47.534
It's not like that.

265
00:16:47.534 --> 00:16:50.164
I'm with Mari because I love her.

266
00:16:50.164 --> 00:16:55.394
Kondo-san, where were you
this morning at nine?

267
00:16:55.394 --> 00:16:57.044
This morning?

268
00:16:57.514 --> 00:16:59.744
I was still asleep.

269
00:16:59.744 --> 00:17:02.284
Can anyone verify that?

270
00:17:02.284 --> 00:17:05.174
I live alone. Of course not.

271
00:17:05.674 --> 00:17:07.504
You don't have an alibi!

272
00:17:07.504 --> 00:17:09.404
So it was you!

273
00:17:09.404 --> 00:17:10.724
Give me my money back!

274
00:17:10.724 --> 00:17:12.184
Hey, calm down!

275
00:17:14.024 --> 00:17:15.434
Are you all right?

276
00:17:15.864 --> 00:17:18.684
I'm feeling a bit exhausted.

277
00:17:19.124 --> 00:17:21.934
You were held captive. It's no surprise.

278
00:17:21.934 --> 00:17:25.064
You should rest for a while.

279
00:17:25.394 --> 00:17:26.724
Excuse me.

280
00:17:26.724 --> 00:17:29.444
I'll take you home.

281
00:17:30.084 --> 00:17:31.344
Thank you.

282
00:17:33.304 --> 00:17:36.584
I'm so glad Manabu-san didn't
have a single scratch on him.

283
00:17:37.154 --> 00:17:41.114
Since he was tied up, I was
worried he'd been assaulted.

284
00:17:48.094 --> 00:17:51.304
Yamashiro Hot Springs Kosoyu

285
00:17:51.594 --> 00:17:54.434
Hattori Shrine

286
00:18:05.514 --> 00:18:07.444
What are you planning to do with the money?

287
00:18:10.104 --> 00:18:11.574
What are you doing here?

288
00:18:11.914 --> 00:18:14.654
We followed you.

289
00:18:14.654 --> 00:18:16.444
Why?

290
00:18:16.444 --> 00:18:22.834
I noticed you were lying
about the kidnapping.

291
00:18:23.114 --> 00:18:26.844
That money you're holding proves it!

292
00:18:26.844 --> 00:18:29.464
I just happened to find this.

293
00:18:29.464 --> 00:18:31.264
Don't lie to me!

294
00:18:31.264 --> 00:18:34.134
You made up the whole kidnapping!

295
00:18:34.134 --> 00:18:36.394
I didn't do that.

296
00:18:36.624 --> 00:18:40.104
Why aren't there any rope
burns on your hands?

297
00:18:40.104 --> 00:18:42.144
Weren't both of your hands tied?

298
00:18:42.494 --> 00:18:45.154
They just disappeared because
some time has passed.

299
00:18:45.154 --> 00:18:48.814
No. You were never tied
up in the first place.

300
00:18:49.244 --> 00:18:54.924
If you look closely at this photo, you
can see your back reflected in it.

301
00:18:55.414 --> 00:18:59.204
You're just holding your hands
behind you. You're not tied up.

302
00:19:01.894 --> 00:19:08.004
It's too bad, but you can't
deceive the eyes of Mori Kogoro.

303
00:19:08.404 --> 00:19:11.304
I'm the one who noticed that.

304
00:19:11.304 --> 00:19:14.574
It just looks that way because of the light.

305
00:19:14.574 --> 00:19:20.004
Mister, did you know everyone's ears are
a different shape, just like fingerprints?

306
00:19:20.004 --> 00:19:22.314
What? What are you talking about?

307
00:19:22.524 --> 00:19:26.834
The security cameras caught the culprit
carrying off the ransom money.

308
00:19:26.834 --> 00:19:31.474
Their face is disguised,
but their ears are visible.

309
00:19:31.474 --> 00:19:36.704
If their shape matches yours, then
we'll know if you're the kidnapper.

310
00:19:37.094 --> 00:19:39.204
Or will you still make excuses?

311
00:19:42.484 --> 00:19:45.324
Manabu, you're unbelievable.

312
00:19:45.324 --> 00:19:47.834
How could you repay my kindness like this?

313
00:19:48.184 --> 00:19:50.414
This is your fault!

314
00:19:50.414 --> 00:19:52.844
You withheld my retirement pay!

315
00:19:53.074 --> 00:19:56.054
You can tell the police all about it.

316
00:19:56.054 --> 00:19:58.724
Damn it! I'm not being arrested!

317
00:20:08.604 --> 00:20:09.694
Stop!

318
00:20:11.344 --> 00:20:13.114
Dad, are you okay?

319
00:20:14.164 --> 00:20:16.444
This is the weight of 30 million yen.

320
00:20:16.974 --> 00:20:19.114
Don't be stupid.

321
00:20:29.584 --> 00:20:30.374
It's so good.

322
00:20:30.704 --> 00:20:33.514
Dad, mind your manners.

323
00:20:34.414 --> 00:20:39.134
Thank you for treating us
to such a luxurious meal.

324
00:20:39.344 --> 00:20:42.254
My 30 million yen was returned to me.

325
00:20:42.254 --> 00:20:44.144
This is nothing.

326
00:20:44.434 --> 00:20:47.104
But Manabu-san escaped.

327
00:20:47.864 --> 00:20:49.874
The local police are looking for him.

328
00:20:49.874 --> 00:20:52.154
It's a matter of time before he's caught.

329
00:20:52.734 --> 00:20:54.274
Damn that Manabu.

330
00:20:54.774 --> 00:20:57.224
I'll clock him good when they arrest him.

331
00:20:57.784 --> 00:21:02.164
By the way, Manabu-san mentioned something
about his retirement pay when he ran.

332
00:21:02.164 --> 00:21:03.164
What was that about?

333
00:21:03.524 --> 00:21:09.434
He was probably talking about how my dad
reduced Manabu-san's retirement pay.

334
00:21:09.434 --> 00:21:10.414
Really?

335
00:21:10.954 --> 00:21:13.824
He got himself injured and then quit.

336
00:21:13.824 --> 00:21:16.944
But didn't he get injured on the job?

337
00:21:16.944 --> 00:21:18.984
You're just a kid! What do you know?

338
00:21:18.984 --> 00:21:22.634
I'm the one who suffered
losses from his injury!

339
00:21:23.104 --> 00:21:25.184
S-Sorry...

340
00:21:26.724 --> 00:21:29.734
Good night.

341
00:21:31.334 --> 00:21:32.814
I'm stuffed.

342
00:21:32.814 --> 00:21:34.654
A lot happened today.

343
00:21:34.654 --> 00:21:36.044
Yeah.

344
00:21:36.044 --> 00:21:38.794
The rest is the police's job.

345
00:21:38.794 --> 00:21:43.294
Let's go home, get some sleep, and
go sightseeing again tomorrow.

346
00:21:43.294 --> 00:21:44.244
Yeah.

347
00:21:44.244 --> 00:21:47.634
But before returning to the hotel, let's
get some ramen to round off the night!

348
00:21:47.634 --> 00:21:50.074
What?! You're going to eat more?

349
00:21:50.074 --> 00:21:51.804
Of course!

350
00:21:53.874 --> 00:21:54.964
Let's go!

